value: Breeds in northern Europe and northern Asia from northern Norway, northern Russia and the southern edge of the Siberian tundra, south to Belgium, northern Germany, Novgorod, southern Urals, southeastern Altai, southwestern Transbaikalia, Amur River, Sakhalin, Kamchatka and the northern Kuriles. Winters throughout Africa, India, Ceylon, south- eastern Asia, Japan, Philippines, and the Malay Archipelago to Australia.
